63/000149315224049098/forms-1a.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">registration statement</a>.</p> <p>WGRX provides pharmaceutical distribution services to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1434361182/image_1434361182.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743712-wellgistics-health-pursues-micro-ipo-plan", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 02:05:01"}, {"id": "4743471", "title": "Disney: Give Me Hope, Moana", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fairy Tale inside baloons\" data-id=\"625812814\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">\u0130lker \u00c7eki\u00e7/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em><strong>Hat Tip to<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gimme_Hope_Jo%27anna\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Eddy Grant</a> for inspiration on the title.</strong></em></p> <p>In the recent past, we have stayed in the neutral zone on Disney (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DIS\" title=\"The Walt Disney Company\">DIS</a></span>). In fact, our last bearish piece was in 2021, when </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625812814/image_625812814.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743471-disney-give-me-hope-moana", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 02:00:00"}, {"id": "4743706", "title": "Iron Mountain: Well-Run REIT, Overpriced For Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman working on digital tablet in dark server room\" data-id=\"885295724\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Erik Isakson</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I rate <b>Iron Mountain Incorporated</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IRM\" title=\"Iron Mountain Incorporated\">IRM</a></span>) as a \u201cHold,\u201d for REIT investors looking for long-term buy and hold investments. The most <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IRM\">important factors</a> that influence my opinion of the REIT are:</p> <ul> <li>Share price is currently overvalued based</li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885295724/image_885295724.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743706-iron-mountain-well-run-reit-overpriced-for-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 01:44:29"}, {"id": "4743704", "title": "Toll Brothers: Rating Upgrade To Buy On Better Fundamentals", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Smiling mid adult woman using social media on smart phone\" data-id=\"1600944330\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">10'000 Hours</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Overview</h2> <p>I wrote about Toll Brothers (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOL\" title=\"Toll Brothers, Inc.\">TOL</a></span>) previously (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718569-toll-brothers-stock-valuation-already-priced-in-near-term-upside\">on 2nd September</a>) with a hold rating, as the valuation was not cheap, despite my view that demand remains strong. I have upgraded my rating from hold to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1600944330/image_1600944330.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743704-toll-brothers-rating-upgrade-to-buy-on-better-fundamentals", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 01:28:01"}, {"id": "4743703", "title": "SMDV Has High Exposure In Banks And Lags Competitors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Small Cap write on sticky notes isolated on Office Desk. Stock market concept\" data-id=\"1256967959\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">syahrir maulana</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>This article updates my </em><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4654182-smdv-dividend-growth-etf-with-a-bank-problem\"><em>review of SMDV published one year ago</em></a><em>, in light of the current portfolio and recent performance.</em></p> <h2><strong>SMDV strategy</strong></h2> <p><b>ProShares Russell 2000 Dividend Growers ETF</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">BATS:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMDV\" title=\"ProShares Russell 2000 Dividend Growers ETF\">SMDV</a></span>) was launched on 02/03/2015 and tracks</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743703-smdv-has-high-exposure-in-banks-and-lags-competitors", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 01:24:07"}, {"id": "4743702", "title": "How Investors Should Assess The Potential Walgreens Buyout", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Walgreens\" data-id=\"458977889\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">RiverNorthPhotography</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>With around two weeks left until the tax-loss selling opportunity ends, Walgreens Boots Alliance (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WBA\" title=\"Walgreens Boots Alliance, Inc.\">WBA</a></span>) unexpectedly soared by 18% to nearly $11.00 on December 10, 2024. The WSJ reported that Walgreens and Sycamore Partners <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4383274-walgreens-jumps-on-report-of-talks-to-sell-itself-to-sycamore-partners\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4383274-walgreens-jumps-on-report-of-talks-to-sell-itself-to-sycamore-partners\" target=\"_blank\">held discussions about a</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743702-how-investors-should-assess-the-potential-walgreens-buyout", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 01:19:35"}, {"id": "4743700", "title": "ImmunityBio's Cash Burn And Dilution Dampen Anktiva's Potential", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Red liquid in drinking glass\" data-id=\"1272819028\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5765px\" height=\"5295px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Knowles</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>My last update on <b>ImmunityBio, Inc. </b>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBRX\" title=\"ImmunityBio, Inc.\">IBRX</a></span>) followed the FDA-approval of Anktiva (nogapendekin alfa inbakicept) for the treatment of BCG-unresponsive non-muscle invasive bladder cancer (NMIBC). I conducted a discounted cash flow analysis that valued Anktiva at $2.3 billion (net present value) based on a 50% market share</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743700-immunitybios-cash-burn-and-dilution-dampen-anktivas-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 01:11:11"}, {"id": "4743699", "title": "Nvidia: Earnings Fail To Impress Again", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nvidia headquarters in Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1547214730\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://s